      - Engineered a real-time analytics dashboard (**React**, **Vite**)
        monitoring **OEE** and throughput across **60+** synchronous production
        lines, sustaining **60 FPS** on legacy hardware.
      - Designed a Zero-Trust multi-tenant architecture isolating operational
