      highlights:
      - Authored and published quantitative findings in the Journal of Student
        Research (JSR) as a peer-reviewed preprint.
      - Applied rigorous statistical modeling techniques to analyze the
        correlation between early-game gold differentials and ultimate match win
        rates.
